com.microsoft.office.sfb.appsdk

Interface HistoryService


  • public interface HistoryService
    This interface manages items that have occurred in the conversation such as previous messages sent or received, or participants joined or left, etc.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ObservableList<ConversationActivityItem> getConversationActivityItems()
      Gets the conversation activity items collection.

    • Method Detail

      • getConversationActivityItems

        ObservableList<ConversationActivityItem> getConversationActivityItems()
        Gets the conversation activity items collection. The collection is returned as an observable list. Callers are expected to register with the collection for notifications by providing an implementation of the callback interface ObservableList.OnListChangedCallback.
        Returns:
        ObservableList of type ConversationActivityItem. An empty collection is returned if there are no conversation activity items present.
        See Also:
        ObservableList, ConversationActivityItem, MessageActivityItem, ParticipantActivityItem
